data.description: Welcome to country living, a peaceful setting in a quiet neighborhood with a beautiful view of the mountain range to the west and bluffs to the east. Easy access to main roads leading to Falcon, Colorado Springs and modern day amenities. This sprawling 2090 Square foot ranch-style home is situated on 5.01 acres, it has plenty of room for pets of all sizes. 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, large living room and a great room for dining or extra space for the kids to play. Master bedroom has new carpet, a newly renovated walk-in shower and a large double closet. Jack and Jill bedrooms with a newly renovated bathroom with a tub. The last bedroom also has its own bathroom with a walk in shower which has been recently renovated as well. New carpet in the all the bedrooms and living room. Large home office has French doors for privacy. The sliding glass entry door has a beautiful view of Pikes Peak. The Dining room along with all the bathrooms and laundry room have the same new vinyl flooring. The refrigerator, dishwasher, range/oven, washer and dryer included. Large 12x16 covered deck located on the eastside facing the bluffs is perfect for family get togethers. Metal roofing and new gutters installed in 2020. Oversized 28'x36' garage with an 8' high door for your taller vehicles, concrete floor and lighting throughout, equipped with 220 volt outlet for the automotive or woodworking enthusiast.
